<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ja">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>akhiLow 3D World Assets</title>
  <style>
    :root {
      --bg: #101014;
      --card: #1a1a21;
      --card-light: #23232c;
      --text: #f4f1ea;
      --muted: #b7b0a3;
      --accent: #d69a4b;
      --accent-dark: #a86f2e;
      --border: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08);
    }

    * {
      box-sizing: border-box;
    }

    body {
      margin: 0;
      font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", sans-serif;
      background:
        radial-gradient(circle at top left, rgba(214, 154, 75, 0.12), transparent 32rem),
        var(--bg);
      color: var(--text);
      line-height: 1.6;
    }

    a {
      color: inherit;
      text-decoration: none;
    }

    .container {
      width: min(1080px, calc(100% - 32px));
      margin: 0 auto;
    }

    header {
      padding: 56px 0 36px;
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
    }

    .site-title {
      margin: 0;
      font-size: clamp(2rem, 5vw, 4rem);
      letter-spacing: 0.02em;
      line-height: 1.1;
    }

    .site-subtitle {
      margin: 14px 0 28px;
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: 1.05rem;
    }

    .header-buttons,
    .card-buttons {
      display: flex;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      gap: 12px;
    }

    .button {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      min-height: 44px;
      padding: 0 18px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      background: var(--card-light);
      color: var(--text);
      font-weight: 700;
      transition: transform 0.18s ease, background 0.18s ease, border-color 0.18s ease;
    }

    .button.primary {
      background: var(--accent);
      color: #19120a;
      border-color: transparent;
    }

    .button:hover {
      transform: translateY(-2px);
      border-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.22);
    }

    .button.primary:hover {
      background: #e3aa5a;
    }

    main {
      padding: 40px 0 64px;
    }

    .section-title {
      margin: 0 0 20px;
      font-size: 1.6rem;
    }

    .product-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, minmax(0, 1fr));
      gap: 24px;
    }

    .product-card {
      overflow: hidden;
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: 22px;
      background: linear-gradient(180deg, var(--card-light), var(--card));
      box-shadow: 0 18px 40px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.22);
      transition: transform 0.18s ease, border-color 0.18s ease;
    }

    .product-card:hover {
      transform: translateY(-4px);
      border-color: rgba(214, 154, 75, 0.45);
    }

    .product-image {
      width: 100%;
      aspect-ratio: 16 / 9;
      object-fit: cover;
      display: block;
      background: #2a2a33;
    }

    .placeholder {
      display: grid;
      place-items: center;
      width: 100%;
      aspect-ratio: 16 / 9;
      background:
        linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(214, 154, 75, 0.16), transparent),
        #25252e;
      color: var(--muted);
      font-weight: 700;
      letter-spacing: 0.04em;
    }

    .product-body {
      padding: 22px;
    }

    .product-title {
      margin: 0 0 8px;
      font-size: 1.3rem;
    }

    .product-desc {
      margin: 0 0 14px;
      color: var(--muted);
    }

    .price {
      margin: 0 0 18px;
      font-weight: 800;
      color: var(--accent);
    }

    .about {
      margin-top: 48px;
      padding: 28px;
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: 22px;
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.035);
    }

    .about h2 {
      margin: 0 0 10px;
      font-size: 1.4rem;
    }

    .about p {
      margin: 0;
      color: var(--muted);
    }

    footer {
      padding: 28px 0;
      color: var(--muted);
      border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
      font-size: 0.9rem;
    }

    @media (max-width: 720px) {
      header {
        padding-top: 40px;
      }

      .product-grid {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      }

      .button {
        width: 100%;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <header>
    <div class="container">
      <h1 class="site-title">akhiLow 3D World Assets</h1>
      <p class="site-subtitle">VRChat / Unity向け3D空間素材</p>
      <div class="header-buttons">
        <a class="button primary" href="https://akhilow.booth.pm/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Boothを見る</a>
        <a class="button" href="https://vrchat.com/home/user/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">VRChatを見る</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </header>

  <main>
    <div class="container">
      <h2 class="section-title">Products</h2>

      <section class="product-grid" aria-label="商品一覧">
        <article class="product-card">
          <img class="product-image" src="images/classroom.jpg" alt="教室パックのスクリーンショット" />
          <div class="product-body">
            <h3 class="product-title">教室パック</h3>
            <p class="product-desc">学校・教室向けの3D空間素材</p>
            <p class="price">価格：〇〇円</p>
            <div class="card-buttons">
              <a class="button primary" href="#" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">商品ページを見る</a>
            </div>
          </div>
        </article>

        <article class="product-card">
          <img class="product-image" src="images/cozy-cafe.jpg" alt="Cozy Cafeのスクリーンショット" />
          <div class="product-body">
            <h3 class="product-title">夜更けの喫茶店 - Cozy Cafe -</h3>
            <p class="product-desc">夜の喫茶店ワールド素材</p>
            <p class="price">価格：〇〇円</p>
            <div class="card-buttons">
              <a class="button primary" href="https://akhilow.booth.pm/items/7587358" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">商品ページを見る</a>
              <a class="button" href="https://vrch.at/zqar9sdk" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">VRChatで見る</a>
            </div>
          </div>
        </article>

        <article class="product-card">
          <div class="placeholder">Coming Soon</div>
          <div class="product-body">
            <h3 class="product-title">次回作</h3>
            <p class="product-desc">制作予定の3D空間素材</p>
            <p class="price">Coming Soon</p>
            <div class="card-buttons">
              <a class="button" href="#">詳細</a>
            </div>
          </div>
        </article>

        <article class="product-card">
          <div class="placeholder">In Progress</div>
          <div class="product-body">
            <h3 class="product-title">制作中</h3>
            <p class="product-desc">現在制作中のワールド・背景素材</p>
            <p class="price">Coming Soon</p>
            <div class="card-buttons">
              <a class="button" href="#">詳細</a>
            </div>
          </div>
        </article>
      </section>

      <section class="about">
        <h2>About</h2>
        <p>Blender / Unityで制作した3Dワールド・背景素材です。VRChatやUnityプロジェクトで使いやすい空間素材を制作しています。</p>
      </section>
    </div>
  </main>

  <footer>
    <div class="container">© akhiLow</div>
  </footer>
</body>
</html>
